    Such shipGroup then gets assigned points
    Then we define which ships belong to this shipGroup.
    We can define a shipGroup which is a existing name in the CCP static data dump invGroups table.
    We can define specif ships which are existing names in the invTypes table of CCP's static data dump.

    If specific names are defined these will be removed from other listings.
